#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can get a list of functions by using this command in a shell: "
#| "<userinput><command>dcop</command> <option>kmail KMailIface</option></"
#| "userinput>. Some documentation is also available in <filename>kdenetwork/"
